{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8eb8c7c1ee","title":"中共中央关于封建富农土改后政治权利问题给东北局的批复","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7b6c8ed9b7","index":0,"year":1949,"month":12,"day":3,"articleId":"8eb8c7c1ee"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e3dd24d7ec","type":"title","text":"中共中央关于封建富农土改后政治权利问题给东北局的批复","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8eb8c7c1ee"},{"id":"3e445312df","type":"appellation","text":"东北局并告华北局：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8eb8c7c1ee"},{"id":"0f9c4e0178","type":"paragraph","text":"十一月三十日电悉。对于封建富农在土地改革后的政治权利，可根据弼时同志报告处理。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8eb8c7c1ee"},{"id":"c1af661048","type":"paragraph","text":" 中央十二月三日","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8eb8c7c1ee"},{"id":"fce9755bda","type":"paragraph","text":"附：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8eb8c7c1ee"},{"id":"c717bc3c5a","type":"subtitle","text":"东北局关于富农在土改后政治权利的处理意见的请示","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8eb8c7c1ee"},{"id":"1a412b6124","type":"subtitle","text":"（一九四九年十一月三十日）","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8eb8c7c1ee"},{"id":"6b9a7bfd05","type":"appellation","text":"中央：","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8eb8c7c1ee"},{"id":"f41a037ff0","type":"paragraph","text":"《共同纲领》中规定，对反动分子、封建地主、官僚资本家剥夺政治权利，未提富农。土地改革时，已没收了富农的土地财产，似亦应剥夺其政治权利。可否根据弼时同志报告，从按照《土地法大纲》，实行土地改革彻底完成的时期算起，满三年一贯服从政府法令政策，安分守己、勤劳生产、表现好者，经审查可恢复其公民权，年限不满与表现不好者则无公民权。如何，请示复。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8eb8c7c1ee"},{"id":"76b07097af","type":"paragraph","text":" 东北局十一月三十日","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8eb8c7c1ee"}],"page":{"id":"8d5504ae90","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8eb8c7c1ee","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}